## Frontend Design Philosophy

The interface is a trading tool, not a marketing site.

**Priorities:**

- clarity
- speed
- low distraction

**Theme:**

| Element | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Background (deep) | #0F1217 |
| Surface / panels | #161B22, #1C2526 |
| Primary text | #F0F4F8 |
| Secondary text | #A0AEC0 |
| Gold accent | #FBBF24 / #FFD700 |
| Positive (green) | #34D399 |
| Negative (red) | #F87171 |
| Impact MEDIUM | #FBBF24 (amber) |

**Rules:**

- no heavy animations
- fast loading
- readable on mobile
- price displayed to 2 decimal places
- **Typography:** 14–16px base; font-weight 500–600; key numbers 18–24px; line-height 1.5–1.6; high-contrast text (#F0F4F8 min)

